IT Technical Support Senior Staff - CIKARANG - PT AJE Indonesia
IT Technical Support Senior Staff - CIKARANG  -
IT Technical Support Senior Staff - CIKARANG
Responsibilities
Responsible for the basic problems handling of:• Provide support and troubleshooting for software & hardware upgrading that includes installation, configuration and troubleshooting of office computer systems, network and applications• Operating System (Microsoft Family, Linux)• Office Application (Microsoft Office, Libre Office)• Communication product support (PABX, VoiP, LAN & WAN, Wireless, Active Directory, Intranet and Internet)• Email profile creation and management (Microsoft Outlook, Outlook Express, Thunderbird)• Antivirus Support (update patch, clearing viruses, health check)• Update Windows and Office patch for end user• Printer driver installation and configuration• Develop hardware documentation and software license• Microsoft Windows Server (Active Directory, Remote Desktop) Requirements:• Candidate should be hardworking, active, self confident, have good problem solving skills, interpersonal• Communication skill, and ability to work under pressure• Deep Knowledge in Network and Hardware will be an added advantage.• Able to work in a team.• Fresh graduates are encouraged to apply.• Candidate should have knowledge on electrical basic• Having 2-3 years experience will be an advantage Candidate must possess at least a Bachelor's Degree, Computer Science/Information Technology or equivalent.Required skill(s): troubleshoot hardware & software, communication product support, email profile creation and management, antivirus support, operating system & office application, Microsoft Windows Server.Required language(s): English and Bahasa Indonesia. Know Spanish would be an advantage.At least 3 year(s) of working experience in the related field is required for this position.Applicants must be willing to work in Lippo Cikarang.Preferably Supervisor / Coordinators specializing in IT/Computer - Hardware or equivalent.Full-Time position(s) available.
